data.description: ONE STORY Great 3/2 Single Family Home with 1 car garage in a gated community with a low HOA. Oasis south gate opens to Palm Aire Country Club. If you love to GOLF this could be paradise , no mandatory membership.  Live 15 minutes from the beach. This house was built in 1997 .Vaulted ceilings , separate laundry room, community pool just a block away ,GYM and more ! Small beautiful complex . An easement and a canal is in the back. This house has NO neighbors in the back. Screened patio, split  floor plan. HOA includes all amenities plus internet, HD cable and law maintenance in the back yard. NEW ROOF from 2021. NEW gourmet  kitchen with a 60"professional gas range ,2 dishwashers ,triple sink,40" subzero refrigerator. OK to rent. Pets are welcome.
